Uses of Package
suncertify.domain

  • Packages that use suncertify.domain 
    Package Description
    suncertify.business
    This package, and its sub-packages, make up the services layer of application which is responsible for parsing and passing data between the persistence and presentation layer of the application.
    suncertify.business.rmi
    This package is part of the services layer of application.
    suncertify.domain
    Provides the domain objects used to query and transfer contractor data between the different layers of the application.
    suncertify.ui
    This package makes up the the presentation layer of the application.
    suncertify.util
    Contains miscellaneous utility classes for the application.
